    "The shape operators L X ∈ 𝔤 are traceless because G ⊂ SL(𝔫), thus H = 0.",
    "Also, since G ⊂ Aut(𝔫), for each b ∈ U i there is an isomorphism of metric Lie algebras φ(b): (𝔫, h) → (𝔫, h b), with (𝔫, h) a nilsoliton with constant -1 2.",
    "The Ricci endomorphism is thus 2h b -1 Ric h b = φ(b) -1 βφ(b) = β,independent of b. Invariantly, this means that it is ∇ ad -parallel.",
    "We now prove that g satisfies (1) for a vector field X satisfying (iii) in Ansatz 3.1.",
    "We first analyse Equation (16a)."
